{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Stranger Things &#8211; Serial Netflix Tentang Dunia Lain Yang Menegangkan","content":"<p>Kalau kamu mengikuti hal-hal yang lagi <em>happening</em> di <em>world’s pop culture</em> saat ini, nama “Stranger Things” mungkin pernah Kamu dengar di internet. Serial ‘<em>horror sci-fi</em>’ ini bakal memasuki <em>season</em> keduanya pada 27 Oktober 2017 nanti, yang bertepatan juga dengan Halloween di Amerika Serikat. <em>Trailer-</em>nya sudah beredar di Youtube, dan gokil abis! Seru. Lengkap dengan <em>background</em> musik legendaris “Thriller”dari The King Of Pop Michael Jackson.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10752\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10752\" data-attachment-id=\"10752\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/3-89/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-43.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screencap trailer “Stranger Things 2”. (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Screencap trailer “Stranger Things 2”. (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-43.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-43.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10752\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/3-43.jpg\" alt=\"Screencap trailer “Stranger Things 2”. (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Screencap trailer “Stranger Things 2”. (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sekuel pertamanya memang sukses, terbukti Netflix sampai membuat season keduanya. Tapi sebenarnya serial ini tentang apa? Kenapa bisa sukses yah? <em>Well</em>, saya tidak berniat dan berminat merusak rasa penasaran kamu dengan spoiler. Tapi saya juga gak pengen Kamu bertanya-tanya “apa sih Stranger Things itu?”. Jadi saya akan mencoba memberikan sedikit gambaran, dan selanjutnya keputusan ada di tangan Kamu.</p>\n<p>“Stranger Things” adalah serial TV kabel Netflix dari Amerika Serikat yang dibuat oleh sepasang saudara kembar, Matt Duffer dan Ross Duffer (populer dengan sebutan “The Duffer Brothers”). Mengambil lokasi kota kecil fiktif Hawkins, Indiana di Amerika Serikat, cerita dimulai pada tanggal 6 November 1983.</p>\n<p>Seorang anak laki-laki bernama Will Byers hilang saat pulang bermain dari rumah temannya Michael / Mike Wheeler.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10755\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10755\" data-attachment-id=\"10755\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/4-81/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-40.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mike (kiri) dan Will (kanan). (Sumber gambar: dorkshelf.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mike (kiri) dan Will (kanan). (Sumber gambar: dorkshelf.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-40.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-40.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10755\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4-40.jpg\" alt=\"Mike (kiri) dan Will (kanan). (Sumber gambar: dorkshelf.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10755\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mike (kiri) dan Will (kanan). (Sumber gambar: dorkshelf.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sementara di kota Hawkins (yang kecil dan terpencil di Indiana) terdapat sebuah instalasi militer pemerintah berkedok bagian dari Kementerian Energi, yang melakukan eksperimen rahasia yang melibatkan percobaan pada objek manusia, aktivitas paranormal ataupun supernatural.</p>\n<p>Hilangnya Will Byers diikuti dengan kemunculan seorang anak perempuan misterius berambut nyaris gundul dengan ekspresi datar, kosakatanya yang minim serta <em>tattoo</em> bertuliskan angka “11” (Mike menyebutnya dengan sebutan “El” yang merupakan singkatan dari “Eleven”) di lengannya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10758\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10758\" data-attachment-id=\"10758\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/5-69/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-33.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Eleven / El dari “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: hellogiggles.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Eleven / El dari “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: hellogiggles.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-33.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-33.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10758\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-33.jpg\" alt=\"Eleven / El dari “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: hellogiggles.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10758\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Eleven / El dari “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: hellogiggles.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sejak Will Byers menghilang, Mike Wheeler bersama El dan dua temannya, Dustin Henderson serta Lucas Sinclair, berusaha mencari keberadaan Will yang misterius.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10749\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10749\" data-attachment-id=\"10749\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/2-66/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-27.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lucas, Dustin, Mike dan El. (Sumber gambar: denofgee.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Lucas, Dustin, Mike dan El. (Sumber gambar: denofgee.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-27.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-27.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10749\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-27.jpg\" alt=\"Lucas, Dustin, Mike dan El. (Sumber gambar: denofgee.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10749\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lucas, Dustin, Mike dan El. (Sumber gambar: denofgee.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sementara ibu Will, Joyce, stress sejak hilangnya Will, mulai mendengar suara-suara dan melihat tanda-tanda aneh di sekitar yang seakan-akan berasal dari Will yang menghilang tanpa jejak. Kisah kemudian mengalir dan akan membuka tabir misterius penyebab hilangnya Will Byers yang berhubungan dengan aktivitas paranormal serta kekuatan <em>“psychokinetic”</em> dari si anak gadis misterius, 11 alias El.</p>\n<h3>Jadi sebenarnya apa yang membuat “Stranger Things” sangat populer dan menjadi hits?</h3>\n<p>Selain tema “<em>horror science fiction</em>” yang digunakan, menurut saya ada aspek lain yang membuat Stranger Things menjadi keren, yaitu penggunaan kultur yang populer di tahun 80an. Mulai dari musik dan film yang saat tahun 80an digemari, sampai ke kebiasaan anak-anak di era itu (kalian harus lihat sepeda yang mereka gunakan, sulit menemukan model sepeda seperti itu sekarang).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10761\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10761\" data-attachment-id=\"10761\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/6-52/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-26.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sepeda klasik era 80an. (Sumber gambar: npr.org)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sepeda klasik era 80an. (Sumber gambar: npr.org)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-26.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-26.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10761\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/6-26.jpg\" alt=\"Sepeda klasik era 80an. (Sumber gambar: npr.org)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10761\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sepeda klasik era 80an. (Sumber gambar: npr.org)</p></div></p>\n<p>Cerita horor berbalut fiksi ilmiah adalah sebuah kisah yang pastinya menarik, menegangkan serta membuat penasaran. Jadi kalau kamu belum pernah nonton sinetron “Stranger Things” ini, saya sangat merekomendasikannya. <em>Worth it</em>. Saya malah nontonnya marathon aka binge-watching aka non stop 8 episode.</p>\n<p>Tapi awas jantungan ya! Karena ada beberapa <em>scene</em> yang cukup menyeramkan. Tapi ada juga yang bakal bikin ngakak. Misalnya ini,</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10746\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10746\" data-attachment-id=\"10746\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/stranger-things-serial-netflix-tentang-dunia-lain-yang-menegangkan/attachment/1-89/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-43.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screencapture “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: personal)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Screencapture “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: personal)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-43.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-43.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10746\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/1-43.jpg\" alt=\" Screencapture “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: personal)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-10746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><br />Screencapture “Stranger Things”. (Sumber gambar: personal)</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Well, have fun and be terrified watching</em> “Stranger Things”! Setelah nonton <em>season</em> 1 nya, mungkin Kamu akan tertarik nonton <em>season</em> 2 nya nanti.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"29d97bd4-ef07-5bd8-ba9d-953f41e977f2"}}}